At least one killed and nine people in a critical condition after a taxi collided with a bakkie head-on near Leratong hospital in Roodepoort on Tuesday.Reports from the scene indicate that several people are were trapped in the wreckage including the deceased who is believed to be the driver of the bakkie.According to Netcare911 paramedics the accident happened at around 05:55am on Tuesday.Meanwhile motorists are advised to avoid the R41 near Impala road in Witpoortjie, Roodepoort.-TNA Reporter 